Properties.Value: This Workflow retrieves customer data from Snowflake, formats and maps it, then creates customers in Shopify. It logs success or error status for each customer creation based on the Shopify API response.

Name: Snowflake To Shopify Customers
Description: This Workflow retrieves customer data from Snowflake, formats and maps it, then creates customers in Shopify. It logs success or error status for each customer creation based on the Shopify API response.
